VALIDATION_SCHEMA:
{
  "definitions": {},
  "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
  "$id": "http://example.com/root.json",
  "type": "object",
  "title": "The Root Schema",
  "required": [
    "serviceName",
    "agentAirlineCode",
    "departureDate",
    "origin",
    "destination",
    "cabinClass",
    "tripType",
    "passenger",
    "airlineCode"
  ],
  "properties": {
    "serviceName": {
      "$id": "#/properties/serviceName",
      "type": "string",
      "title": "The Servicename Schema",
      "default": "",
      "examples": [
        "flightSearch"
      ],
      "pattern": "^(.*)$"
    },
    "agentAirlineCode": {
      "$id": "#/properties/agentAirlineCode",
      "type": "string",
      "title": "The Agentairlinecode Schema",
      "default": "",
      "examples": [
        "ACE"
      ],
      "pattern": "^(.*)$"
    },
    "departureDate": {
      "$id": "#/properties/departureDate",
      "type": "string",
      "title": "The Departuredate Schema",
      "default": "",
      "examples": [
        "2019-05-20"
      ],
      "pattern": "^(.*)$"
    },
    "origin": {
      "$id": "#/properties/origin",
      "type": "string",
      "title": "The Origin Schema",
      "default": "",
      "examples": [
        "MAA"
      ],
      "minLength": 1,
      "maxLength": 3,
      "pattern": "^(.*)$"
    },
    "destination": {
      "$id": "#/properties/destination",
      "type": "string",
      "title": "The Destination Schema",
      "default": "",
      "examples": [
        "DPS"
      ],
      "minLength": 1,
      "maxLength": 3,
      "pattern": "^(.*)$"
    },
    "cabinClass": {
      "$id": "#/properties/cabinClass",
      "type": "string",
      "title": "The Cabinclass Schema",
      "default": "",
      "examples": [
        "E"
      ],
      "minLength": 1,
      "pattern": "^(.*)$"
    },
    "tripType": {
      "$id": "#/properties/tripType",
      "type": "string",
      "enum": [
        "O",
        "R"
      ],
      "title": "The Triptype Schema",
      "default": "",
      "examples": [
        "O"
      ],
      "pattern": "^(.*)$"
    },
    "passenger": {
      "$id": "#/properties/passenger",
      "type": "object",
      "title": "The Passenger Schema",
      "required": [
        "ADT"
      ],
      "properties": {
        "ADT": {
          "$id": "#/properties/passenger/properties/ADT",
          "type": "integer",
          "title": "The Adt Schema",
          "default": "",
          "examples": [
            "1"
          ],
          "minimum": 1.0
        }
      }
    },
    "airlineCode": {
      "$id": "#/properties/airlineCode",
      "type": "array",
      "title": "The Airlinecode Schema",
      "items": {
        "$id": "#/properties/airlineCode/items",
        "type": "string",
        "title": "The Items Schema",
        "default": "",
        "examples": [
          "I5"
        ],
        "minLength": 1,
        "pattern": "^(.*)$"
      }
    }
  }
}
